snippet.title: Aquaman 2 facing INSTANT REGRET! Amber Heard seriously damaging films hype and potential box office!
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 has officially begun filming, and the reaction online has to be raising eyebrows at Warner Studios! The backlash from bringing back Amber Heard might not have been a wise decision. Will the Johnny Depp situation hurt the DC Comics movie bottom-line?
